      "title": "A 15-foot-tall ganja tree was seized",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Haliela Police arrested a suspect yesterday (13) along with a 15 feet high cannabis tree that was grown in the garden of a house in the Uva Deegalle area of \u200b\u200bHaliela.",
        "A 63-year-old resident of Uva Deegalle, Haliela has been arrested. According to information received by the police, during a raid, the suspect was arrested with this ganja tree, which was grown in a small half-barrel among the mana bushes in the suspect's garden."
      ],
